emuInput.TitMainTitle: Car, driven by Robert Ziegler, with extensive front end damage and broken windshield, from accident with trailer truck, another version
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 17, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "Smashup - A trailer truck driven by Jack Boun, 1068 Blackadore Street, collided with this machine driven by Robert Ziegler, 1313 Reedsdale Street, Saturday, causing two passengers, Sallie Turner, and Willa Mae Hightower, to suffer injuries. - Courier Photo."
